table abc_extra193.abc_ABCMeta_check_qualnames:
  description: "abc.ABCMeta check method qualname checks in abcdunders193 namespace — ABCMeta.__instancecheck__.__qualname__=='ABCMeta.__instancecheck__' (len=25: 'ABCMeta'=7+'.'=1+'__instancecheck__'=17=25; __instancecheck__ customizes isinstance() to support virtual subclasses registered via ABCMeta.register()); ABCMeta.__subclasscheck__.__qualname__=='ABCMeta.__subclasscheck__' (len=25: 'ABCMeta'=7+'.'=1+'__subclasscheck__'=17=25; __subclasscheck__ customizes issubclass() to check virtual subclass relationships); ABCMeta.__instancecheck__.__qualname__ (25) == ABCMeta.__subclasscheck__.__qualname__ (25) — tied as the longest qualnames in this spec; both are length 25 because __instancecheck__ and __subclasscheck__ are the same character count (17); verified with Python 3.14.3"
  kind: python_call_eq
